                    <b> Payment Rules and Regulations: </b><br />
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        1. Admission Fee (ADM) must be paid before the child enters the school for the first time. This is a one-time payment only and is non-refundable. <br />
                        2. The school’s tuition fee must be fully paid every month/ term/ year at the 1st - 10th of every month. The school reserves the right to impose lateness penalty for any lateness and outstanding. <br />
