                        leaving date. When the form is not returned, you will need to pay next month’s fees. <br />
                        5. Lateness and Outstanding Penalty: <br />
                        - Late and outstanding charges of Rp. 100,000/ day are applicable for tuition fees paid after 10th of every month. <br />
                        - A penalty of Rp. 25.000/ hour applies for lateness in pick up time after toleration time (toleration time is 15 minutes after class finish). <br />
                        - Penalty in the form students not receiving end of year report card, portfolios, certificates and not attending classes are applied for late and outstanding Annual Development Fee (ADF) and other fees. <br />
                        6. Method of Payments: <br />
                        - Payment can only be made using unique virtual account number that will be sent to your email address at the end of every month – Please do inform the school (Finance Admin) if you don’t receive the email from our
