                        - Whether you are using ATM, internet banking, or mobile banking from any bank, always use “Transfer” menu. Then put the unique virtual account number stated in your email in the destination account. And put the
                        specific nominal stated in the invoice sent to your email. <br />
                        - A 2,5% bank administration applies for Credit Card (except for BSM Card). <br />
                        7. Please do inform the school beforehand for any inquiries regarding payment matters. The school is welcome to help you and suggest you solutions regarding your financial matters.
